805
00:59:27,949 --> 00:59:30,762
I'll sing you lullabies before bed every night,

806
00:59:31,593 --> 00:59:33,715
and I'll be a good husband,

807
00:59:33,715 --> 00:59:35,421
staying with you for the rest of my life.

808
00:59:48,624 --> 00:59:49,624
No.

809
00:59:51,588 --> 00:59:52,588
Huh?

810
00:59:53,660 --> 00:59:54,660
Why?

811
00:59:56,328 --> 00:59:59,227
You have proposed to me several times already.

812
00:59:59,227 --> 01:00:01,704
This time, I'm going to propose to you.

813
01:00:01,704 --> 01:00:04,039
Just like when I asked you to marry me
when I was younger.

814
01:00:13,386 --> 01:00:14,647
Will you marry me?

815
01:00:21,777 --> 01:00:24,246
So, you're really going to
take this cat home, right?

816
01:00:25,952 --> 01:00:26,952
Sure.

817
01:00:27,576 --> 01:00:31,884
