818
01:00:31,884 --> 01:00:35,610
♫ That split second when I saw you ♫

819
01:00:35,610 --> 01:00:37,555
I love you, Prim.

820
01:00:37,555 --> 01:00:39,660
I love you too.

821
01:00:39,660 --> 01:00:42,876
♫ It felt like the world slowed down ♫

822
01:00:42,876 --> 01:00:46,988
♫ The moment of falling in love
Feels just like this ♫

823
01:00:46,988 --> 01:00:51,107
♫ That fleeting instant when we met ♫

824
01:00:51,107 --> 01:00:54,864
♫ The moment we connected,
the moment our eyes met ♫

825
01:00:54,864 --> 01:00:58,176
♫ I wish I could freeze this time forever ♫

826
01:00:58,176 --> 01:01:02,410
♫ In this moment, I love you ♫

827
01:01:05,887 --> 01:01:08,193
Hey, is the boss really going to resign?

828
01:01:08,193 --> 01:01:10,617
Go get Thee back to work, no matter what.

829
01:01:10,617 --> 01:01:14,318
If you can't,
I'll cut ties with both you and your son.

830
01:01:14,318 --> 01:01:16,866
What do you want me to do?
I'm stuck in the middle here.

831
01:01:16,866 --> 01:01:19,541
In this matter, you have to pick a side.

832
01:01:19,541 --> 01:01:22,741
I know you want to achieve your goals first,

833
01:01:22,741 --> 01:01:24,712
but I also want you to love yourself.

834
01:01:24,712 --> 01:01:26,352
I'll try to do that.

835
01:01:26,352 --> 01:01:29,290
So, who did they appoint
as the new Vice President after me?

836
01:01:29,290 --> 01:01:32,846
That's actually why I'm here today.
